---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base
  title="Programs — Global Faith Temple"
  description="Past initiatives, current programs, future plans, and the daily activities that hold our work together."
>
  <main>

    <header class="relative bg-ivory pb-16 pt-40 md:pb-24 md:pt-48">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 text-center">
        <p class="fade-up mb-6 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-olive opacity-80">Programs</p>
        <h1 class="fade-up font-serif text-4xl leading-[1.1] text-olive-deep md:text-6xl">
          Work undertaken<br />in steady hands.
        </h1>
        <p class="fade-up mx-auto mt-8 max-w-2xl text-base leading-relaxed md:text-lg" style="color: rgba(43,42,29,0.78);">
          What we have already done in remembrance, what we are tending today, what we hope yet to do — and the small, faithful activities that hold every week of the temple together.
        </p>
        <div class="fade-up mt-12 flex items-center justify-center gap-3 text-olive opacity-50">
          <span class="h-px w-10" style="background: rgba(74,76,33,0.4);"></span>
          <svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 10 10"><circle cx="5" cy="5" r="1.4" fill="currentColor" /></svg>
          <span class="h-px w-10" style="background: rgba(74,76,33,0.4);"></span>
        </div>
        <nav class="fade-up mt-10 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-x-6 gap-y-2 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-olive opacity-70">
          <a href="#past" class="hover:text-olive">Past</a><span class="opacity-30">·</span>
          <a href="#current" class="hover:text-olive">Current</a><span class="opacity-30">·</span>
          <a href="#future" class="hover:text-olive">Future</a><span class="opacity-30">·</span>
          <a href="#activities" class="hover:text-olive">Weekly</a>
        </nav>
      </div>
    </header>

    <!-- Past -->
    <section id="past" class="scroll-mt-24 border-t py-20 md:py-28" style="border-color: rgba(74,76,33,0.1);">
      <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-6xl gap-12 px-6 md:grid-cols-12">
        <div class="reveal-left md:col-span-4">
          <p class="mb-4 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-olive opacity-70">Past initiatives</p>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl leading-tight text-olive-deep md:text-4xl">What we carry forward in memory.</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal-right md:col-span-8">
          <ul class="stagger space-y-6">
            <li class="fade-up border-l pl-5" style="border-color: rgba(74,76,33,0.3);">
              <p class="font-serif text-lg text-olive-deep">2014 — Light of Return</p>
              <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--muted-foreground);">A multi-year program reuniting veterans of the United States, Korea, Australia, and the Republic of Vietnam with sister communities along the Mekong.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="fade-up border-l pl-5" style="border-color: rgba(74,76,33,0.3);">
              <p class="font-serif text-lg text-olive-deep">2017 — Hands of the Harvest</p>
              <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--muted-foreground);">Food and elder-care partnerships established across three provinces, serving veterans' widows and the families who tend them.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="fade-up border-l pl-5" style="border-color: rgba(74,76,33,0.3);">
              <p class="font-serif text-lg text-olive-deep">2019 — Letters Home</p>
              <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--muted-foreground);">A correspondence project between students of seven nations and veteran elders — letters offered in eight languages, kept in our archive.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="fade-up border-l pl-5" style="border-color: rgba(74,76,33,0.3);">
              <p class="font-serif text-lg text-olive-deep">2021 — Quiet Hours</p>
              <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--muted-foreground);">Opening the sanctuary as a daily refuge throughout the pandemic — a candle lit each dawn, a door kept open each dusk.</p>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Current -->
    <section id="current" class="scroll-mt-24 border-t py-20 md:py-28" style="border-color: rgba(74,76,33,0.1); background-color: var(--parchment);">
      <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-6xl gap-12 px-6 md:grid-cols-12">
        <div class="reveal-left md:col-span-4">
          <p class="mb-4 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-olive opacity-70">Current programs</p>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl leading-tight text-olive-deep md:text-4xl">The work in our hands today.</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal-right md:col-span-8">
          <div class="stagger grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2">
            <div class="fade-up border-t pt-4" style="border-color: rgba(74,76,33,0.2);">
              <p class="font-serif text-lg text-olive-deep">Candle of Remembrance</p>
              <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--muted-foreground);">A candle lit each daybreak for the soldiers of eight nations, with a weekly Hour of Remembrance at week's end.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="fade-up border-t pt-4" style="border-color: rgba(74,76,33,0.2);">
              <p class="font-serif text-lg text-olive-deep">Veterans' Companionship</p>
              <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--muted-foreground);">Visits, calls, and shared meals with veterans and their families — wherever they are, whatever they need.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="fade-up border-t pt-4" style="border-color: rgba(74,76,33,0.2);">
              <p class="font-serif text-lg text-olive-deep">Bridges to Vietnam</p>
              <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--muted-foreground);">Exchanges, scholarships, and joint observances with sister sanctuaries in Huế, Đà Nẵng, and Hồ Chí Minh City.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="fade-up border-t pt-4" style="border-color: rgba(74,76,33,0.2);">
              <p class="font-serif text-lg text-olive-deep">Open Sanctuary</p>
              <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--muted-foreground);">Long days of open doors — no programming, no expectation. Only space, and stillness, and the candle.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="fade-up border-t pt-4" style="border-color: rgba(74,76,33,0.2);">
              <p class="font-serif text-lg text-olive-deep">Study Circles</p>
              <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--muted-foreground);">Small gatherings for reading, reflection, and gentle conversation across history, faith, and reconciliation.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="fade-up border-t pt-4" style="border-color: rgba(74,76,33,0.2);">
              <p class="font-serif text-lg text-olive-deep">Care Network</p>
              <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--muted-foreground);">A confidential support line for grief, gratitude, and quiet need — staffed by listeners trained in patience.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Future -->
    <section id="future" class="scroll-mt-24 border-t py-20 md:py-28" style="border-color: rgba(74,76,33,0.1);">
      <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-6xl gap-12 px-6 md:grid-cols-12">
        <div class="reveal-left md:col-span-4">
          <p class="mb-4 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-olive opacity-70">Future plans</p>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl leading-tight text-olive-deep md:text-4xl">Quietly taking shape.</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal-right md:col-span-8">
          <ol class="stagger space-y-6">
            <li class="fade-up flex gap-6">
              <span class="font-serif text-2xl text-olive opacity-50">01</span>
              <div>
                <p class="font-serif text-lg text-olive-deep">A Garden of Names</p>
                <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--muted-foreground);">A living memorial within the sanctuary grounds — each tree planted in the name of a fallen soldier, by a hand that loved them.</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="fade-up flex gap-6">
              <span class="font-serif text-2xl text-olive opacity-50">02</span>
              <div>
                <p class="font-serif text-lg text-olive-deep">Youth Stewardship</p>
                <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--muted-foreground);">A year-long program for young people drawn to service, remembrance, and the long quiet work of peace.</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="fade-up flex gap-6">
              <span class="font-serif text-2xl text-olive opacity-50">03</span>
              <div>
                <p class="font-serif text-lg text-olive-deep">Heritage Archive</p>
                <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--muted-foreground);">Gathering letters, photographs, and oral histories from the veterans and families of all eight nations, so the record never thins.</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="fade-up flex gap-6">
              <span class="font-serif text-2xl text-olive opacity-50">04</span>
              <div>
                <p class="font-serif text-lg text-olive-deep">Sister Sanctuary Network</p>
                <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--muted-foreground);">Extending our circle of partner temples and memorial communities across Asia, the Pacific, and the Americas.</p>
              </div>
            </li>
          </ol>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Weekly activities -->
    <section id="activities" class="scroll-mt-24 border-t py-20 md:py-28" style="border-color: rgba(74,76,33,0.1); background-color: var(--beige);">
      <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-6xl gap-12 px-6 md:grid-cols-12">
        <div class="reveal-left md:col-span-4">
          <p class="mb-4 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-olive opacity-70">Weekly</p>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl leading-tight text-olive-deep md:text-4xl">A week in the life of the temple.</h2>
          <p class="mt-4 text-sm" style="color: var(--muted-foreground);">All gatherings are open. There is no fee, and no expectation. Come as you are; leave when peace says so.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal-right md:col-span-8">
          <ul class="stagger divide-y border-y" style="border-color: rgba(74,76,33,0.15);">
            <li class="fade-up grid grid-cols-12 items-baseline gap-4 py-4 md:py-5">
              <span class="col-span-4 font-serif text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-olive md:col-span-2">Sunday</span>
              <span class="col-span-8 font-serif text-sm tracking-wide md:col-span-2" style="color: rgba(43,42,29,0.7);">8:30 AM</span>
              <span class="col-span-12 font-serif text-xl text-olive-deep md:col-span-8">Morning Reflection</span>
            </li>
            <li class="fade-up grid grid-cols-12 items-baseline gap-4 py-4 md:py-5">
              <span class="col-span-4 font-serif text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-olive md:col-span-2">Sunday</span>
              <span class="col-span-8 font-serif text-sm tracking-wide md:col-span-2" style="color: rgba(43,42,29,0.7);">10:30 AM</span>
              <span class="col-span-12 font-serif text-xl text-olive-deep md:col-span-8">Gathering Service</span>
            </li>
            <li class="fade-up grid grid-cols-12 items-baseline gap-4 py-4 md:py-5">
              <span class="col-span-4 font-serif text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-olive md:col-span-2">Monday</span>
              <span class="col-span-8 font-serif text-sm tracking-wide md:col-span-2" style="color: rgba(43,42,29,0.7);">6:00 PM</span>
              <span class="col-span-12 font-serif text-xl text-olive-deep md:col-span-8">Study Circle</span>
            </li>
            <li class="fade-up grid grid-cols-12 items-baseline gap-4 py-4 md:py-5">
              <span class="col-span-4 font-serif text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-olive md:col-span-2">Wednesday</span>
              <span class="col-span-8 font-serif text-sm tracking-wide md:col-span-2" style="color: rgba(43,42,29,0.7);">7:00 PM</span>
              <span class="col-span-12 font-serif text-xl text-olive-deep md:col-span-8">Evening Prayer for Peace</span>
            </li>
            <li class="fade-up grid grid-cols-12 items-baseline gap-4 py-4 md:py-5">
              <span class="col-span-4 font-serif text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-olive md:col-span-2">Thursday</span>
              <span class="col-span-8 font-serif text-sm tracking-wide md:col-span-2" style="color: rgba(43,42,29,0.7);">10:00 AM</span>
              <span class="col-span-12 font-serif text-xl text-olive-deep md:col-span-8">Veterans' Tea</span>
            </li>
            <li class="fade-up grid grid-cols-12 items-baseline gap-4 py-4 md:py-5">
              <span class="col-span-4 font-serif text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-olive md:col-span-2">Friday</span>
              <span class="col-span-8 font-serif text-sm tracking-wide md:col-span-2" style="color: rgba(43,42,29,0.7);">12:00 PM</span>
              <span class="col-span-12 font-serif text-xl text-olive-deep md:col-span-8">Hour of Remembrance</span>
            </li>
            <li class="fade-up grid grid-cols-12 items-baseline gap-4 py-4 md:py-5">
              <span class="col-span-4 font-serif text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-olive md:col-span-2">Saturday</span>
              <span class="col-span-8 font-serif text-sm tracking-wide md:col-span-2" style="color: rgba(43,42,29,0.7);">9:00 AM</span>
              <span class="col-span-12 font-serif text-xl text-olive-deep md:col-span-8">Open Sanctuary</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
</Base>
